{"tid":1526687,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"前線Ios手足自救神器 - Shortcut","createTime":"2019-09-01T07:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T07:02:34.000Z","uid":79351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2e72ed9498c6125ac52815efa2338906ae843e16","tid":1526687,"uid":79351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每次有手足被捕都會聯絡唔到律師<br />\n主因係無人知你地已經被捕<br />\n有d醒目d既會係記者面前大叫自己咩名<br />\n但無記者既話就...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左盡量避免依個情況<br />\n用Iphone既全部馬上安裝<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Shortcut</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馬上安裝Shortcut</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馬上安裝Shortcut</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馬上安裝Shortcut</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首先去App Store搵<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Shortcut</span></span><br />\n之後跟足以下步驟一步一步setup<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 1.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MvWfk6T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMvWfk6T.jpg&h=ec2ec430&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n按<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">製作捷徑</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 2.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gozTSdX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgozTSdX.jpg&h=46585cf9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nSearch message之後按下<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">傳送訊息</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 3.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0HNm07Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0HNm07Q.jpg&h=e0dbd100&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n收件人就輸入自己信得過既朋友電話<br />\n最好輸入2-3個,以防訓著睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事前記得同人交代聲先<br />\n內容唔好唔好唔好淨係講你已經被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得要留低你中英名全名及身份證number</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得熄左執行時顯示</span></span><br />\n按完成下方<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">設定</span></strong>既icon<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 4.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3swCzuh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3swCzuh.jpg&h=c21efaad&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n按<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加入到Siri</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 5.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jnJmgJK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjnJmgJK.jpg&h=b225fb01&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n按<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅色點</span></span>錄音<br />\n記得唔好派膠set 任何口號<br />\n例如光復香港或時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你個fd多得你條戇鳩唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後右上角完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咁不幸被捕只要大叫<br />\n&quot;喂,Siri&quot;之後再叫錄音既指令就會直接send msg<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出發前要set定同試下次work唔work先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望唔會有人用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A:</span></span><br />\nQ1. 點解叫極Siri都唔應?<br />\nA1. 睇下開左Siri未同埋mon要向上<br />\n<br />\nQ2.現場咁嘈點收音?<br />\nA2.所以最好有Apple Watch. 無既就用你叫口號既力大叫啦<br />\n<br />\nQ3.用parachute有咩分別?<br />\nA3.未用過,手上無資料答你唔到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好睇完就算,幫手正評同推上熱門</span></span>"},{"pid":"5e896dd72162777b34ef724b043ae12e1a806a7d","tid":1526687,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"caf778f488cc3795d28b6abeb556efe99b3b9794","tid":1526687,"uid":79351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:02:34.000Z","msg":"麻煩推呢個post<br />\n依個post開錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1526692/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1526692/page/1</a>"}]}